text: Airbnb’s new logo found in a trademark book from 1988 Thursday, 10 September 2015 (3 minutes ago) Around a year ago, Airbnb updated its logo to something a little different. At the time, commenters noted how unique the logo was, and more importantly, that it kind of sort of looks reminiscent of a part of the female anatomy that you might not want to use for your company logo.
